.el .ds Aq '
.TH dkp-run 1  "run 0.1.2" 
.SH NAME
dkp\-run \- Invoke a WASM/WASI procedure from machine/procedures/
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdkp run\fR [\fB\-\-input\fR] [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-timeout\-ms\fR] [\fB\-\-allow\-unsigned\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-audience\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIPACK\fR> <\fIPROCEDURE\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Invoke a WASM/WASI procedure from machine/procedures/
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-input\fR \fI<JSON>\fR
JSON object to pass as stdin to the procedure (default: {})
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: plain]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
plain: Human\-readable plain text (default)
.IP \(bu 2
table: Aligned table using comfy\-table
.IP \(bu 2
json: Pretty\-printed JSON
.RE
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress informational output; print only results
.TP
\fB\-\-timeout\-ms\fR \fI<MS>\fR
Override the wall\-clock timeout in milliseconds
.TP
\fB\-\-allow\-unsigned\fR
Allow running non\-WASM procedures from unsigned bundles (dev/testing only)
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print debug info (schema paths, provider calls, etc.)
.TP
\fB\-\-audience\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Filter content to assets tagged for a specific audience profile
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
<\fIPACK\fR>
Path to the DKP bundle directory
.TP
<\fIPROCEDURE\fR>
Procedure ID (stem name without extension, e.g. "macro\-calc")
.SH VERSION
v0.1.2
